<h1>Logging In To PMOG</h1>
<h5>Sometimes the First and Hardest Task</h5>

<br />

<div class="help">
  <dl>
    <dt>PMOG Extension Login</dt>

    <dd>
      If you are having problems logging in to PMOG, here are some steps you can take to remedy the problem:
      <br/>
      <br/>
      - Your stored passwords may be corrupt. Try overwriting them by hand using the 'New Login' option in the Login menu:
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <center>
        <img src="/images/help/new-login.png" alt="enter the credentials for a new PMOG login" width="402" height="194" border='1'>
      </center>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      - Clear your stored passwords for PMOG and try again. Note that doing this will require you to re-enter the passwords for any and all of your PMOG accounts:
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <center>
        <img src="/images/help/delete-stored-passwords.png" alt="clear your stored PMOG passwords" width="403" height="212" border='1'>
      </center>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      - For all other PMOG login problems, try <a href='/sessions/find/'>resetting your password</a> and if that fails to work, <a href='/about/contact/'>get in touch</a>.
    </dd>
  </dl>

  <p align="center"><a href="/help/toolbar">More Toolbar Help</a></p>

</div>